# 🖼️ Image Classification with CNN — CIFAR-10

A Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) built with TensorFlow/Keras to classify images from the CIFAR-10 dataset into 10 categories. Trained and evaluated entirely in Google Colab.

---

## 📸 Sample Predictions

> Green = Correct Prediction &nbsp;|&nbsp; Red = Wrong Prediction

